(2291, 233, 'liste_2_droite', '- What are the possible types of organizational arrangements?\r\n\r\n- What are the factors weighing on organizational choices?\r\n\r\n- What are the links between concrete work modes (division, coordination, etc.) and the other key variables (power distribution, objectives, contextual factors, etc.)?\r\n\r\n- How does one switch organizational types?\r\n\r\n- How generate the minimum convergence needed between the project for change and the very transformation process?\r\n\r\n- Etc.'),
